But Cindy has claimed that they were simply one-offs and that there is unlikely to be a similar phenomenon to the early nineties modelling career again. 

Nowadays, take a quick glance at the magazine section in any newsagent and you will find scores of singers and reality stars  staring back at you. 

This month, Kim Kardashian is on the cover of Australian Vogue and Sienna Miller graced the front of the British edition in December. 

 

